      "assetDescription": "<p>apxUSD is a synthetic dollar issued by Apyx and backed by preferred shares of Digital Asset Treasuries (DATs), which generate off-chain dividend income to support the broader Apyx ecosystem. apxUSD itself does not accrue yield; instead, it functions as the protocol\u2019s primary liquidity layer, designed to provide deep secondary market liquidity and broad integration across DeFi and CeFi venues.</p>\n<p>The protocol also utilizes Protocol-Owned Liquidity (POL) as a liquidity buffer to help support apxUSD stability, particularly during periods of market stress. Dividend income from the underlying DAT preferred shares is not distributed to apxUSD holders, but is instead directed toward apyUSD, Apyx\u2019s yield-bearing savings asset.</p>",
